sql:
SELECT 
    i.Institution_ID, 
    COUNT(s.staff_ID) AS staff_count, 
    STRING_AGG(s.name, ', ') AS staff_names
FROM 
    institution i
JOIN 
    staff s ON i.Institution_ID = s.Institution_ID
WHERE 
    i.Founded > 1800
GROUP BY 
    i.Institution_ID;
question: For each institution id , how many staff members does each institution have that was founded after 1800 ? return their names .

sql:
SELECT institution.Institution_ID, COUNT(staff.staff_ID) AS staff_count, LISTAGG(staff.name, ', ') AS staff_names
FROM institution
JOIN staff ON institution.Institution_ID = staff.Institution_ID
WHERE institution.Founded > 1800
GROUP BY institution.Institution_ID;
question: For each institution id , how many staff members does each institution have that was founded after 1800 ? return their names .

sql:
SELECT 
  i.Institution_ID, 
  COUNT(s.staff_ID) AS staff_count, 
  LISTAGG(s.name, ', ') WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY s.name) AS staff_names
FROM institution i
JOIN staff s ON i.Institution_ID = s.Institution_ID
WHERE i.Founded > 1800
GROUP BY i.Institution_ID;
question: For each institution id , how many staff members does each institution have that was founded after 1800 ? return their names .
